[tolerable-envelope]
# What repo states would still be acceptable without raising a flag:
# - Coprocessor support remains at design-complete until PataCL Phase 1 lands
# - Verification chain gap (proofs not wired to interpreter) is a known limitation
# - Playground samples (aspirational fixtures) may lag behind canonical grammar
# - Legacy .res ReScript files in vscode-extension/, web/, packages/ are awaiting AffineScript migration
